        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The filling is a cooked custard rather than a buttercream: egg yolks, butter, and sugar over a bain-marie until thick, then stirred off the heat with chopped pecans, raisins, coconut, and bourbon. It needs to cool fully before going between the layers; warm filling soaks into the cake and the layers slide. The "
          },
          {
